## Leadership & Founder

### Rev. Dr. Steve Mensah - General Overseer & Founder

Rev. Steve Mensah is the General Overseer of the Charismatic Evangelistic Ministry (CEM) in Accra, Ghana. He is one of the Great Sons of Ghana the Lord has raised and is using greatly to affect lives not only in Ghana but round the world. He is a great conference speaker on Evangelism, Prayer, the Word and many more. His Apostolic Ministry has taken him to continents and nations round the world to bless and strengthen the body of Christ.

**Personal Qualities:**
- Humble servant of God loved by many colleagues and Pastors
- Simple, peace-loving nature and openness to all persons
- Very approachable regardless of social status or standing
- Compassionate, kind, loving with a large heart for the poor and needy
- Passionate about reaching the unsaved and neglected, especially in rural areas

**Ministry Focus:**
- Spearheads the "Christ to the Rural World Ministry" bringing "Jesus to the Rurals"
- Conducts rural outreaches with free medical help, drugs, food, clothing, Bibles and books
- Empowers the poor to change their situation and environment
- Focuses on youth empowerment to make a difference in their generation
- Teaches on Sweet Melodies FM radio

**Published Books:**
